+# REAL-10 Narrow Ratification For REAL-11
+
+Date: 2026-05-15
+
+This ratifies REAL-10 only as clean, pinned, audited controlled market
+evidence. Forbidden / not ratified claims include spontaneous market emergence,
+causal performance gain, live REAL-6B, model ranking, price-as-truth, and
+real-world readiness.
+
+## Evidence Hygiene
+
+Canonical conclusion-bearing evidence:
+
+```text
+handover/evidence/real8x_market_ab_clean_20260515T141331Z
+```
+
+This clean directory is the only conclusion-bearing REAL-10 evidence for
+REAL-11 planning and reports.
+
+Contaminated/remediation-only evidence:
+`handover/evidence/real8x_market_ab_20260515T134453Z` is invalid for
+conclusions and may be cited only as contamination/remediation context.
+
+## Ratified Claim
+
+REAL-10 is ratified as:
+
+```text
+clean controlled market evidence;
+E1 market visibility for B/C/D;
+market structure active on ChainTape/CAS;
+claim-boundary discipline preserved.
+```
+
+Conclusion-bearing clean data:
+
+```text
+A: market disabled                         market_tx=0   solve=5/15
+B: market visible, no TaskOutcomeMarket    market_tx=10  solve=5/15
+C: TaskOutcomeMarket enabled               market_tx=42  solve=6/15
+D: TaskOutcomeMarket + scripted fixture    market_tx=38  solve=4/15
+buy_with_coin_router=0 in all arms
+```
+
+## Not Ratified
+
+E2 not achieved: no live non-scripted agent-generated router or short-equivalent
+action appears in the clean evidence.
+
+E3 not achieved: role labels and role diversity counters do not prove persistent
+behavioral role differentiation.
+
+E4 not achieved: small-n descriptive evidence does not establish causal
+performance improvement.
+
+Forbidden launch/beta claims unless future evidence satisfies the stated
+threshold:
+
+```text
+forbidden: autonomous prediction market
+forbidden: emergent agent economy
+forbidden: market-proven performance improvement
+forbidden: real-world readiness
+forbidden: agent economy beta without E2 at least once under live non-scripted condition
+forbidden: emergent market beta without E3 persistent role differentiation
+forbidden: launch-ready public launch
+```
+
+## REAL-11 Consequence
+
+REAL-11 must split structural market tx from agent economic action tx. Activity
+alone is not emergence; scripted actions do not satisfy E2.

